These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, western, documentary
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person eating mango is the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | musical     | western   | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
City: berlin, new-york, rome, marseilles
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| City   | rome    | new-york      | berlin | marseilles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
City: liverpool, colone, marseilles, hannover
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| City         | liverpool | hannover | marseilles   | colone |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, domino, chess, whist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing whist##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game   | whist | domino | scrabble  | chess      |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | surfing | basketball |

