.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, kiwi, pineapple
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, dunhill, siglo, fonseca
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | kiwi | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Cigar    | baccarat       | fonseca | siglo | dunhill     |

