.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, mexican, nigerian, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, lacrosse, cycling, weightlifting
1. the mexican is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | nigerian | dutch | mexican |
| Sport           | tennis      | cycling | weightlifting | lacrosse    |

