.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, vegafina, old-henry, dannemann
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the person driving the trike is the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Cigar         | old-henry | cain      | vegafina | dannemann |
| Transport   | car          | quad-bike | tram     | trike    |

