2. the thai is on the right of the turkish##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Nationality    | turkish | thai  | japanese | indonesian |
