.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, cooking, gardening, collecting
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, frog, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Hobby   | cooking | singing | collecting | gardening  |
| Pet           | hedgehog | fish      | frog | ferret |

