2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | camping  | hiking | photography   |
| Pet        | rabbit | lizard | rat    | hamster |

