.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, rock-climbing, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, indie, trance, country
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of trance is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | rock-climbing | video-games | cooking |
| Music-Genre   | country     | trance    | electronic      | indie   |

