.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, blend, havana, cain
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
4. the cain-smoker is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Cigar   | baccarat | havana | blend | cain   |
| Transport     | scooter  | boat    | car       | snowmobile |

 